title: Terra by Battat Lava Mountain T-Rex Adventure Playset - Electronic Dinosaur Toys for Kids Ages 3+ (14 Pieces)
features: Role-playing will allow your child to imagine a Jurassic sized world of fun. With a Tyrannosaurus Rex, volcanic lava mountain, jail cell, action figure, vehicle, and other accessories, this dinosaur playset creates a playtime filled with action and adventure.

This 14-piece electronic dinosaur playset is the perfect activity for a fun adventure. The set includes 1 large electronic dinosaur, 1 medium dinosaur, 1 mini dinosaur, 1 4x4 vehicle, 1 volcano, 1 rock, 1 dinosaur skull, 1 ladder, 1 rope, 1 axe, 1 wire fire, 1 torch, 1 action figure, and 1 dinosaur egg.
This Lava Mountain T-Rex Adventure from Terra by Battat encourages your child to engage in creative storytelling while reducing screen time.
The electronic T-Rex will roar as its eyes light up during play! Complete with movable parts. Includes 3x AG13 (1.5V) batteries.
Suitable for children ages 3 years and up.
description: Let your little one lead a wildlife safari while playing with this African Elephant Family from Terra by Battat. Elephants will march and come to life while your child plays with these detailed elephant figurines. The family of elephants has realistic details, including lifelike trunks, tusks, and large ears. Add to your collection of other jungle animals from Terra by Battat. Your little one’s imagination can run wild while creating a zoo, safari, or wildlife refuge with this elephant herd. Did you know African elephants are the largest mammals on the planet? Turn playtime into an educational learning experience when you read through the fun and interesting facts about elephants included on the packaging. This African Elephant Family makes the perfect gift for your little one’s birthday or other holiday celebration! Recommended for children ages 3 and up.
